umes](https://docs.railway.com/volumes).\n\nI also updated the “Ready For Build” and acceptance criteria to reflect this: first build `but-agentlog` projection API, then a generator-service proof, then Forge as a thin facade. The symlink is still uncommitted, as requested.","tool_name":null,"tool_input":null,"source_record":{"timestamp":"2026-05-24T16:08:51.178Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"message","role":"assistant","phase":"final_answer"}}}